{{Year nav topic5|2001|Estonian television}}
This is a list of [[Television in Estonia|Estonian television]] related events from 2001.

==Events==
*3 February - [[Tanel Padar]] and [[Dave Benton]] are selected to represent Estonia at the [[Eurovision Song Contest 2001|2001 Eurovision Song Contest]] with their song "[[Everybody (Tanel Padar and Dave Benton song)|Everybody]]". They are selected to be the seventh Estonian Eurovision entry during Eurolaul held at the ETV Studios in Tallinn.
*12 May - Estonia wins the 46th [[Eurovision Song Contest 2001|Eurovision Song Contest]] in [[Copenhagen]], [[Denmark]]. The winning song is "[[Everybody (Tanel Padar and Dave Benton song)|Everybody]]", performed by [[Tanel Padar]] and [[Dave Benton]].

