'''Bia West''' is one of the [[Constituency|constituencies]] represented in the [[Parliament of Ghana]]. It elects one [[Member of Parliament|Member of Parliament (MP)]] by the [[first past the post]] system of election. Bia West is located in the [[Bia District]] of the [[Western Region, Ghana|Western Region]] of [[Ghana]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ghanaelections.peacefmonline.com/pages/2016/western/214/|title=Ghana Election 2016 Results - Bia West Constituency|last=FM|first=Peace|website=Ghana Elections - Peace FM|access-date=2018-04-14}}</ref>
