'''Bossembélé Airport''' {{Airport codes|BEM|FEFL}} was an [[airstrip]] located within [[Bossembélé]], a town in the [[Ombella-M'Poko]] prefecture of the [[Central African Republic]]. Mature trees now overhang the former runway.
