'''Ersfjorden''' is a [[fjord]] in the [[Tromsø]] municipality of [[Norway]].<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://snl.no/Ersfjordbotn|title=Ersfjordbotn – Store norske leksikon|access-date=2016-07-06}}</ref> It is 12.5 kilometers long and begins on the western side of [[Kvaløya (Tromsø)|Kvaløya]].<ref name=":0" /> 

