[[File:Ljubljana, die evangelische Kirche.JPG|thumb|The Lutheran Church named after [[Primož Trubar]] in [[Ljubljana]], capital of Slovenia.]]
The '''Evangelical Church of the Augsburg Confession in Slovenia''' ({{lang-sl|Evangeličanska cerkev augsburške veroizpovedi v Sloveniji}}) is a [[Lutheran]] denomination in [[Slovenia]]. It is led by Bishop Geza Filo. It is a member of the [[Lutheran World Federation]], which it joined in 1952. It is also a member of the [[Conference of European Churches]] and the [[Community of Protestant Churches in Europe]].

